# Netlify-only (GitHub Pages ignores this file — it resolves clean slugs itself).
# The site links internally with clean slugs (/about, not /about.html). These
# 301s make sure the old extension URLs, and anything already linking to them,
# land on the canonical clean path instead of serving the page at two URLs.
/index.html     /           301!
/about.html     /about      301!
/sonics.html    /sonics     301!
/visuals.html   /visuals    301!
/epk.html       /epk        301!
